subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Tina Thompson scored nine of her 22 points in the fourth quarter to help visiting Houston (8-3) pull away for a 72-58 W.N.B.A. victory against the Liberty last night. Sherill Baker scored 12 points for the Liberty (2-8).
